     <h1 class="title">党史知识题库：判断题（22200字）</h1> 
     <div class="count"> 
      <span class="in-time">发表于：2016.4.18</span>
      <span class="from">来自：www.ttfanwen.com</span>
      <span class="cnt-size">字数：22200 </span>
      <span class="from"><a href="http://m.ttfanwen.com/info_35/fw_4795749.html" rel="nofollow">手机看范文</a></span> 
     </div> 
     <div class="content"> 
      <script>dy('bd_cnt_top_21');</script> 
      <div class="n-p"> 
       <div class="zt-tj"> 
        <a href="http://www.ttfanwen.com/dangshizhishijingsaizongjie/" target="_blank"><img src="http://img.ttfanwen.com/lm/mc_4272.jpg" title="党史知识竞赛总结" /></a> 
       </div> 
